"Redis version and server configuration have a **major** impact on "
"throughput. Using Redis 8.2 with IO threads yields ~6 GB/s reads vs ~1.5 "
"GB/s with Redis 6.0 defaults."
msgstr "Redis 版本和服务器配置对吞吐量有 **重大** 影响。使用 IO 线程的 Redis 8.2 读取速度约为 6 GB/s，而使用 Redis 6.0 默认配置时约为 1.5 GB/s。"

